§ T11-W6+ § specs/grand-vision/17_DISTRIBUTION_STRATEGY.csl
§§ Distribution-Strategy : what's open · what's proprietary · what's server-only · what's encoded
§§ Apocky 2026-05-01 directive : "what files do I actually share/sell/publicize vs what do we keep proprietary/secret/abstracted/encoded?"
§§ status @ ◐ design-pending · enforcement @ wave-8+

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ AXIOMS (¬ negotiable · t∞)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

A-1 : the-MOAT = trained-KAN-weights + substrate-internals + render-pipeline-shaders + Coherence-Engine-eval-fn
A-2 : the-COMMUNITY-VALUE = CSSL-language-spec + csslc-compiler + lore + .csl-examples (open · documented · forkable)
A-3 : the-INFRASTRUCTURE = Stripe-secrets + Supabase-service-role + Apocky-master-key (NEVER on-player-machine)
A-4 : the-PRIVATE = player's-keys + Σ-mask-state + Home-internals + Sensitive<*> (LOCAL-ONLY · NEVER egress)
A-5 : the-PROTOCOL = Σ-Chain-envelopes + monetization-commands + KAN-canary-reports (encoded + signed · server-authoritative)
A-6 : open-source ¬ enables-cloning · proprietary-binaries-where-it-matters protect-the-moat
A-7 : every-distribution-decision documented · transparent-to-player · audit-emit-on-egress

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ TIER-A : OPEN-SOURCE (community + portability + platform-effect)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ FILES @ public-GitHub-repo · MIT-or-Apache-2.0 dual-license · forkable
  ⊑ specs/*.csl                        ← CSL3 language spec · 30+ canonical doc files
  ⊑ specs/grand-vision/*.csl           ← architectural specs (00-16+ all 17 specs)
  ⊑ compiler-cssl/                     ← CSSL self-hosted compiler-bootstrap · public
  ⊑ compiler-rs/crates/csslc/          ← Rust stage-0 compiler binary source · public
  ⊑ compiler-rs/crates/cssl-mir/       ← MIR layer · public
  ⊑ compiler-rs/crates/cssl-parser/    ← parser · public
  ⊑ compiler-rs/crates/cssl-lexer/     ← lexer · public
  ⊑ compiler-rs/crates/cssl-cgen-cpu-cranelift/ ← cranelift backend · public
  ⊑ examples/*.cssl                    ← simple examples (hello_triangle · sdf_shader · audio_callback)
  ⊑ Labyrinth of Apocalypse/main.cssl  ← entry-point scaffold · public-as-tutorial
  ⊑ specs/grand-vision/00..15+_*.csl   ← thesis · paradigms · data-axes · intent · cosmology · etc.
  ⊑ DEPRECATED-The Infinite Labyrinth/GDDs/* ← legacy lore (already public-documentable)
  ⊑ PRIME_DIRECTIVE.md + LICENSE.md + NOTICE.md ← project ethics · legal
  ⊑ basic-host-stub-crates : cssl-host-replay · cssl-host-audit · cssl-host-stereoscopy (utilities · MIT)

§ rationale
  ⊑ open-CSSL-language attracts contributors · enables-community-mods (loot-recipes · cosmetic-themes)
  ⊑ open-csslc enables port-targets (someone-else can-port CSSL to-Mac/Linux/Web)
  ⊑ open-specs document-the-architecture · academic-citation · retention
  ⊑ open-utilities (replay/audit/stereo) build-tooling-ecosystem · NOT the-game-itself
  ⊑ NOTHING here-reveals proprietary-game-logic OR-trained-models OR-render-secrets

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ TIER-B : PROPRIETARY-BINARY (game · ship-as-compiled-only · NO source)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ FILES @ proprietary · ship-as-binary-only · obfuscation @ release-mode
  ⊑ LoA.exe                            ← compiled-final-game · stripped-symbols-at-release
  ⊑ trained-KAN-weights @ proprietary-pack ← .kan-weights-v1 binary · Ed25519-signed
  ⊑ cssl-substrate-omega-field         ← MIT-license-source PRIVATE · ship binary-only
  ⊑ cssl-substrate-kan                 ← MIT-license-source PRIVATE · ship binary-only
  ⊑ cssl-substrate-prime-directive     ← Σ-mask-internals · ship binary-only
  ⊑ cssl-substrate-omega-field implementations ← ship binary-only · spec PUBLIC · IMPL PROPRIETARY
  ⊑ render-shaders · 12-stage-pipeline @ wgsl-internals ← ship-compiled-spirv-only · NOT-readable-source
  ⊑ Coherence-Engine evaluation-fn     ← in-substrate · ship binary-only
  ⊑ 6-novelty-paths (Wave-Unity · Spectral · Fractal-Amp · Gaze-Collapse · HDC-Bound-Lenia · Mise-en-abyme) implementations ← ship binary-only · spec public

§ obfuscation-recipe @ release-build :
  ⊑ rustc -C strip=symbols + LTO + codegen-units=1
  ⊑ wgsl shaders → SPIRV-bytecode + obfuscated-uniform-layout-via-slot-IDs
  ⊑ KAN-weights = packed-blob via cssl-host-asset-bundle LAB-format · BLAKE3-content-hashed · Ed25519-signed
  ⊑ asset-bundle interior-references via SHA256-content-IDs (¬ filenames-leak-info)

§ rationale
  ⊑ trained-models = the-actual-investment · forking-source ¬ replicates-them
  ⊑ Coherence-Engine eval-function specifics are-the-game-feel · ship binary
  ⊑ render-novelty-paths-impls are-the-visual-signature · ship-compiled
  ⊑ players get-game · don't-need source · LICENSE prohibits-reverse-engineering

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ TIER-C : SERVER-ONLY (NEVER on-player-machine · cssl-edge + cssl-supabase)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ FILES @ server-side-only · environment-variables · NEVER bundled-with-game
  ⊑ APOCKY_MASTER_KEY (Ed25519 private)  ← signs hotfix-payloads per spec/16
  ⊑ STRIPE_SECRET_KEY                    ← server-side checkout · webhooks
  ⊑ STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SIGNING_SECRET        ← verifies inbound Stripe events
  ⊑ SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY            ← server-side full-DB-access · bypass-RLS for-admin
  ⊑ federated-learning aggregator-pipeline (Python or Rust binary) ← runs on private-server
  ⊑ KAN training-pipeline + telemetry-aggregator
  ⊑ anti-cheat-heuristics + ban-list
  ⊑ CDN-secrets (CloudFront-distribution-key · etc.)
  ⊑ certificate-private-keys for-domain-TLS

§ vault @ never-in-git
  ⊑ git-secret-scanning enabled @ pre-commit-hook · auto-rejects keys
  ⊑ all-secrets via environment-variables (Vercel-env · Supabase-vault · GitHub-Actions-secrets)
  ⊑ rotation-policy : 90-day rotation for-Stripe + Supabase · 12-month for-Apocky-master · ¬ shared

§ rationale
  ⊑ leaking-master-key = catastrophic (any-player can-sign-fake-hotfix)
  ⊑ leaking-Stripe-key = financial-fraud-vector
  ⊑ leaking-Supabase-service-role = full-DB-takeover

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ TIER-D : PER-PLAYER-PRIVATE (local-only · NEVER egress)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ FILES @ player's-machine · LOCAL-ONLY · cssl-rt enforces structural-non-egress
  ⊑ player's Ed25519-sovereign-keypair  ← generated-locally · NEVER-leaves-machine · stored OS-keychain-or-equivalent
  ⊑ Σ-mask local-state                  ← consent-mask-per-cell · LOCAL-ONLY
  ⊑ Home-dimension full-state           ← per spec/16 TIER-1 · ω-field-cells-reserved-for-Home
  ⊑ Sensitive<biometric|gaze|face|body> ← F5-IFC structurally-refused @ TelemetryEgress::for_domain compile-time
  ⊑ replay-recording (cssl-host-replay) ← NIST-SHA256-hashed · LOCAL by-default
  ⊑ frame-recordings (cssl-host-frame-recorder) ← LFRC-format · LOCAL
  ⊑ companion-history full-text         ← only-derivative-summaries opt-in to cssl-supabase 0004 companion_logs

§ enforcement
  ⊑ F5-IFC type-system blocks-egress @ compile-time · Sensitive<*> structural-refusal
  ⊑ F6-observability path-hash-only · NEVER-raw-content-egresses
  ⊑ cssl-rt OS-keychain-integration (Windows-Credential-Manager · macOS-Keychain · Linux-libsecret)
  ⊑ runtime-audit emits Σ-Chain-egress-attempt event @ ¬ Σ-mask-allowed → halt-with-error

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ TIER-E : OBFUSCATED + ENCODED PROTOCOL (client ↔ server)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ FILES @ over-the-wire · BLAKE3-encoded · Ed25519-signed · idempotent
  ⊑ Σ-Chain-event-envelopes            ← TIER-2 → TIER-3 events per spec/14
  ⊑ monetization-commands              ← Stripe-checkout-intent · battle-pass-tier-claim · gacha-pull-request
  ⊑ KAN-canary disagreement-reports    ← stage-0-vs-stage-1 mismatch-events
  ⊑ Akashic-record-imprints            ← per spec/18 · player's deeds-published-to-shared-memory
  ⊑ federated-bias-aggregate-fetches   ← cohort-baseline-bias-distribution
  ⊑ asset-bundle-streams               ← LAB-v1 chunks · BLAKE3-content-hashed
  ⊑ hotfix-payloads                    ← per spec/16 HF-1..HF-8 · master-signed

§ encoding-stack :
  ⊑ TLS-1.3 transport-layer · cert-pinning per cssl-host-mp-transport-real
  ⊑ Application-layer : BLAKE3-content-hashing · Ed25519-signature-envelopes
  ⊑ Idempotency-keys : every-mutating-request includes UUID-v7 · server dedupes
  ⊑ Schema-validation : all-payloads JSON-schema-validated server-side BEFORE-DB-write
  ⊑ Anti-replay : nonce + timestamp · within ±60s server-time-window

§ rationale
  ⊑ man-in-the-middle attacker can-sniff-but-can't-forge
  ⊑ replay-attacks blocked by-nonce + timestamp
  ⊑ schema-bugs caught BEFORE-DB-write · prevents-malformed-state

