  ⊑ github.com/Apocky/CSSL3-Examples (NEW) ← .cssl-examples · curated · MIT
  ⊑ readthedocs.io OR-mdbook-site for-docs (auto-built from-specs/)

§ private-game-binary @ TIER-B
  ⊑ Steam (primary) ← anti-cheat + DRM via Steamworks · standard-distribution
  ⊑ itch.io (secondary) ← direct-download · Apocky-curated
  ⊑ Epic Games Store (tertiary, optional) ← reach + featured-promo
  ⊑ self-distributed via launcher (MyceliumLauncher)? ← alternate · cssl-edge auto-update-channel · Vercel-CDN
  ⊑ asset-deltas streamed-via-CDN @ release-mode · runtime fetch-on-demand

§ infrastructure @ TIER-C
  ⊑ Supabase (DB + Auth + Realtime + Storage) ← already-architected · production-tier
  ⊑ Vercel (cssl-edge Next.js + API routes) ← already-deployed-stub · production-tier
  ⊑ Stripe (payments + Stripe-Tax) ← per spec/13 monetization
  ⊑ CloudFront-or-equivalent (CDN for-asset-deltas) ← future
  ⊑ Apocky's private-Linux-VPS or-AWS-Lambda for-federated-learning aggregator-pipeline

§ player-local-storage @ TIER-D
  ⊑ %APPDATA%/LoA/ (Windows) · ~/Library/Application Support/LoA/ (macOS) · ~/.local/share/LoA/ (Linux)
  ⊑ contains : Home-dimension state · player-keys (OS-keychain-prefer) · replay-files · frame-recordings · cached-asset-bundles

§ over-the-wire @ TIER-E
  ⊑ HTTPS → Vercel cssl-edge routes
  ⊑ HTTPS + WebSocket-via-Supabase-realtime for-multiplayer-signaling
  ⊑ HTTPS → Stripe checkout-redirects + webhooks
  ⊑ HTTPS → CDN for-asset-bundle-streaming

